Package: rrstools
Title: Analyzing RoboCupRescue Simulation Data
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Keisuke", "Ando",
           email   = "nononoexe@ymail.ne.jp",
           role    = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-4085-2067"))
Description: Tools for analyzing data from RoboCupRescue Simulation (RRS)
    <https://rescuesim.robocup.org>, a disaster rescue simulation platform.
    Supports reading virtual city map and disaster scenario files into
    analyzable data structures and provides functions for their visualization.
